        <li>Apply quantitative analysis and data modeling techniques to interpret research data, write research reports
            and scientific papers.</li>
        <li>Contribute to the development and evaluation of software tools, models, and algorithms.</li>
        <li>Collaborate with other team members to contribute to ongoing research projects and initiatives.</li>
